title: The Last Departure.2015.WEBRip.RR.mp4
description:
Fear and terror reach Northern Air Base 3, a remote airfield in the north country wilderness. On her last flight of the season, Sarah (Kelli Reynolds) awakens an evil that won't let her escape. The reports of missing people, the stories the natives told over the years. They were all true! Sarah finds out first hand, what happens to people that try to leave this place. 

This film does not have an IMDB entry.  It's an Indie production from CampusFilms Studios, who also do not have an IMDB entry!

Enjoy,
RR
